it looks like check_output is available, but during build, somehow it is not.
I would guess this would be something specific to your python setup.

The root cause of your issue is:

val = bytes(subprocess.check_output([
AttributeError: 'module' object has no attribute 'check_output'

I cannot really say why this is happening, since check_output is actually available in your python's subprocess module. At this point, I would say someone more familiar with your python setup or stack overflow (as suggested above) would be the best place to ask.
